This software implements the reach-scan measurement framing: estimating the
future field of a committed reasoning prefix and its target reachability,
developed at Reachability Labs and described in the associated paper(s).

The reach-scan procedure, the source/prefix/projection contract design, and the
foreclosure/target-reachability framing are original contributions of
Reachability Labs.

If you use this instrument or build on the contract, please cite the associated
paper. This is attribution guidance, not a restriction beyond Apache-2.0.
